name: Serena by Eva Cortez
description:
Stormy days, 
Water up to the neck.
Calm and serene.
The sun will rise.

Don't you have days when you feel like you're in over your head? Everything comes together: the good and the not so good too. Circumstances seem adverse and threaten to sink the ship. Even so, keeping faith and calm is the only option, with the certainty that the sun will come out sooner or later. 

2D digital animation on offer. 
Animation resolution 1700px x 2600px in GIF format.

Completion date: November 21, 2021 
Technique: Digital drawing and 2D animation 
Software: Medibang Pain Pro and Photoshop.

The artwork may not be reproduced commercially. The author reserves the right to use the image of the work for merchandising.
